{"tid":1384814,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚都話冇用 點樣先有用?","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:47:26.000Z","uid":51041,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c912b4775100e39e22ed75c91cd383ce1d76a1","tid":1384814,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"你班撚樣又話<br />\n勇武冇用<br />\n集會遊行冇用<br />\n不合作運動冇用<br />\n超合作運動冇用<br />\n登報聯署冇用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係冇用呀<br />\n咁係咪乜都唔做呀？ <br />\n<br />\n話比你地知 <br />\n講一句支持佢地已經好撚有用! <br />\n唔該唔好再潑冷水<br />\n民意要歸邊既已經歸晒 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91d13539a7e708f2674caa12db9a1f8b4279f7a","tid":1384814,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"980cbd23f84df7067ee3ac6c69ce895d7c46f030","tid":1384814,"uid":287376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:01:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48965b9a81e0c33947459aa6ca67c2fb9fee71c0","tid":1384814,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:01:22.000Z","msg":"果d post負皮屌佢兩句就算啦<br />\n成班網軍不停散發失敗論"},{"pid":"0402eab22ee4515c796dccd496a525b005c043c3","tid":1384814,"uid":50565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"中央已經放慢手腳由你地玩，所以做幾多成效都好似唔夠，但如果做嘅事會影響到中國就可能不一樣。<br />\n我發夢見到我地今日攪不合作唔係係調景嶺，而係上水同羅湖，見到一班水貨狗、自由蟲、跨境學童同搵大陸錢嘅香港人，進出不得，真係好慘。<br />\n如果現實有人咁做應該幾大獲。"},{"pid":"f8115b2e870e35d400ae3046e6e7f23ca04452e7","tid":1384814,"uid":231471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"不合作運動被遺忘的人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384816</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b3c10530d683e52818d884c3619f82182f15192","tid":1384814,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbded7eb45339096d91a1b5cbb1097324fbdebdc","tid":1384814,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8392268ec75c966bb6be70c6cb9703a9686863db","tid":1384814,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"塞死埋關口<br />\n千其唔好呀<br />\n好大鑊架<br />\n可能連國內人都關心下到底香港發生咩事<br />\n咁會嚇親人架<br />\n唔好呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e57f39dc7138bcdce5bd0ab6fee5c012362f31b","tid":1384814,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}